The '''462nd ''Volksgrenadier'' Division''' ({{lang-de|462. Volksgrenadier-Division}}) was a ''[[Volksgrenadier]]'' division of the [[German Army (Wehrmacht)|''Heer'']] (German Army) during the [[Second World War]], active from 1942 to 1944.

==Operational history==
{{command structure
|name= Order of Battle, 462nd ''Volksgrenadier'' Division{{sfn|Mitcham|2007|pp=128–129}}
|date=October 1944
